(5, 3, 1, '', '2016-04-05 20:04:02', 46, 4224, '2f45b7f894854d8ca327c113f3aa5ec0abf909a8', '{"id":3,"asset_id":57,"title":"Ready Project","alias":"ready-project","introtext":"<p class=\\"font7\\"><span class=\\"color30\\">When transforming your organisation to\\u00a0your desired image, the design phase is to shape all of the elements to execute your new oganisational image.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"font7\\">\\u00a0This phase brings all of the moving parts together on a single path to transform your organisation. \\u00a0With critical elements such as project management (to plan the activities and manage the technical components of your desired image), change management (engaging the stakeholders to adopt the new image), workflow mapping (mapping the inter-connectedness of the project to all areas of the organisation), and gap analysis (focus on the areas that need attention), you are assured that your transformation will take place.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"font7\\"><img src=\\"images\\/bigstock-Project-management-concept-in--22790042.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"font7\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n","fulltext":"\\r\\n<p class=\\"font7\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"font7\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"font7\\"><span class=\\"color30\\">The components that make up <b><i>Design<\\/i><\\/b> are:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"font7\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"font7\\"><span class=\\"color30\\"><b>Project Plan<\\/b> - a tool that enables you to capture, record and track all of your project activities.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"font7\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"font7\\"><span class=\\"color30\\"><b>Change Management Plan<\\/b> - is a tool that enables you to capture, record and track all of your change management activities; aligned to your project.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"font7\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p class=\\"font7\\"><span class=\\"color30\\"><b>Enterprise Architect<\\/b> - is a tool that enables you to map your business